The,service,provides,a,citation,database,with,references,to,scientific,papers,and,other,publications,It,serves,the,needs,of,researchers,to,find,published,sources,on,topics,and,by,authors,of,interest,to,them,The,site,collects,citations,shares,them,across,scientific,communities,and,provides,for,reviews,of,findings,by,other,researchers,API,methods,support,search,against,the,citation,database,for,term,or,author,name,matches,in,references,to,papers,from,scientific,journals,and,conference,presentations,Methods,also,support,generation,of,bibliography,listings